Yesterday night our dearest friend @Super_Rotti had crossed over the rainbow bridge. You have always been an inspiration to all of us with your winning smile, insatiable character and perseverance. We will miss you always. Your legacy will forever frap on. 🌈❤️
.
For those of you who don't know, Rotti was diagnosed with Spindle Cell Sarcoma and IVDD [one of many things he's powered through], which unfortunately meant Rotti's time was limited. @Queensbeststumpydogrescue and many others created a bucket list where he enjoyed many things most other pups haven't enjoyed yet. Rotti has gone through so much but despite everything, he had chose to continue to live life to the fullest. Thanks for being an inspiration to us all. #LoveYouAlways
